{"id":"428835640537739_528466743907961","type":"status","created_time":"2013-08-25T06:25:27+0000","message":"To,\nThe Prime Minister\nIndia.\n\nsubject: \"hilsha ilisha\" vs \"onion\".\n\nSir,\nI want to tell you that \"hilsha ilisha\" is our national fish and also our national culture.\nso never expect we will supply to you our national culture on contrary of your simple onion.\nkeep your onion to you own, if possible you can play with your onion as a marbel game\nwe will be habituated soon eating vegetable without your tasteless onion.\n\nsincerely yours\nTasnuva Aboni\npure Bengali in Bangladesh."}